 and error monitoring are essential."), mdx("p", null, "One of the most important assets I've gained from this bumpy ride is the confidence that \"I can learn and grow anywhere.\""), mdx("p", null, "Of course, growth could be faster and more efficient for a junior developer to learn in manageable situations, not an early startup. You need a good team and seniors to steep the growth graph."), mdx("p", null, "However, I would say that my time at Moye was valuable in that it confirmed my ability to develop myself even in extreme situations where I was chased by milestones without enough team members, including seniors, and was able to make some contributions to the team and the company."), mdx("h1", {
